metadata.name: Formation 1
metadata.description:
Formation is a fine digital AI-Collaborative art series by Felipe Posada x The Invisible Realm. It blends a decade's worth of digital and analog art practices with the integration of AI, resulting in one-of-a-kind compositions that are further refined and finished by the artist's hand. The series will exist in both digital and physical formats.  

Formation seeks to evoke deep contemplation about humanity's place in the universe, and to draw parallels between infinity being found both outside and inside of us.

NFT Unique 1/1 edition. 
2500x2500px, 150dpi JPG.
